snippet.title: Ma Vie en Rogue Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer video for a new narrative-driven Roguelike RPG! Ma Vie en Rogue will feature fun, engaging gameplay, Ultima Easter eggs, a Lord British character, cloth map, metal ankh amulet, unlimited customizations, and so much more. Check it out!

Kickstarter is closed but Early Access is coming soon to Steam! Wishlist MVR now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3015740/Ma_vie_en_rogue/

Kickstarter campaign: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fschultz/ma-vie-en-rogue?ref=8k1tne
